{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ecc36eff29","title":"国内国际及红军的情况","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f0b945ee7e","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":28,"articleId":"ecc36eff29"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"25d969e7e8","type":"paragraph","text":"国内国际及红军的情况","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ecc36eff29"},{"id":"b459077d09","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月28日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ecc36eff29"},{"id":"630b6d885e","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石还站在中间地位，对日仍力求妥协，但比过去强硬了许多，对我力求缩小苏区打击红军，但已觉得困难，许其部下二陈°与我谈判。潘汉年去南京两次，距离甚远，一时不易成就。我之政策，一方面从人民、从反蒋军阀、从国民党内部造成运动：一方面红军消灭蒋军，双管齐下，追蒋妥协。苏区与红军任务坚持打蒋，不稍放松。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ecc36eff29"},{"id":"23c8a7fee2","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东致彭德怀电的主要内容。[21二陈，指陈果夫、陈立夫。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ecc36eff29"}],"page":{"id":"030945e512","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ecc36eff29","start":23,"end":23}}}},"__N_SSG":true}